creator: HomeExchange
descriptionHtml:
HomeExchange is the world's leading house swap community, with nearly 400,000 homes in 187 countries, allowing users to find a cost-effective and comfortable accommodation solution for their holidays and travel. HomeExchange's innovative system allows for traditional reciprocal home swaps and non-reciprocal exchange with GuestPoints. All HomeExchange members can also benefit from Service Plus, a package of services that help our members travel with peace of mind.

Save time and do more with the HomeExchange mobile app: search available homes, live chat with HomeExchange members, add images of your home directly from your phone.

Download the HomeExchange app now!

Five tips for using the app:

1. Register for free, fill out your personal profile and your home profile
2. Select your dream destinations and add homes to your favorites
3. Contact other members available for a house swap through our integrated messaging system
4. Define the details of your trip and finalize your home exchange
5. Travel with peace of mind and access the home exchange details directly in the app

Comments or questions? Contact us: mobile@homeexchange.com

Follow us on Twitter and Instagram @homeexchangecom
And Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/homeexchangecom/

title: HomeExchange - House Swapping

creator: HomeExchange
descriptionHtml:
HomeExchange is the world's leading house swap community, with nearly 400,000 homes in 187 countries, allowing users to find a cost-effective and comfortable accommodation solution for their holidays and travel. HomeExchange's innovative system allows for traditional reciprocal home swaps and non-reciprocal exchange with GuestPoints. All HomeExchange members can also benefit from Service Plus, a package of services that help our members travel with peace of mind.

Save time and do more with the HomeExchange mobile app: search available homes, live chat with HomeExchange members, add images of your home directly from your phone.

Download the HomeExchange app now!

Five tips for using the app:

1. Register for free, fill out your personal profile and your home profile
2. Select your dream destinations and add homes to your favorites
3. Contact other members available for a house swap through our integrated messaging system
4. Define the details of your trip and finalize your home exchange
5. Travel with peace of mind and access the home exchange details directly in the app
